---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="AgriConnect Smart">
  <main>
    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr] lg:px-8 lg:py-20">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-emerald-700">AI, cybersecurity, and blockchain for circular agriculture</p>
          <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">Turn agricultural waste into health, income, and clean energy.</h1>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg text-slate-600">Farmers sell biomass instead of burning it, industries source traceable feedstock, and health actors monitor regional pollution risk with aggregated environmental data.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="/register" class="rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-emerald-700">Join as Farmer</a>
            <a href="/marketplace" class="rounded-md border border-slate-300 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-50">Explore Marketplace</a>
            <a href="/dashboard/admin" class="rounded-md border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-sky-800 hover:bg-sky-100">View Demo Dashboard</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="min-h-[420px] overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-100 shadow-sm">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1500937386664-56d1dfef3854?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Agricultural field prepared for biomass recovery" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="border-y border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:px-8">
        <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">The problem</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Burning agricultural residues creates smoke, CO2e emissions, and respiratory risk for nearby communities.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">The solution</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">A secure marketplace diverts residues to biomass buyers and tracks carbon and health impact by region.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-950">The demo</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-slate-600">Local AI formulas, Supabase RLS, security logs, and blockchain-style hashes make the MVP realistic and easy to run.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-950">Tech pillars</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold text-emerald-950">AI prediction and risk</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-emerald-900">Price estimates, carbon saved, health benefit scores, and recommendations.</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold text-sky-950">Cybersecurity</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-sky-900">Auth, role-based UI, Supabase RLS, input validation, and anomaly logs.</p></div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5"><h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-950">Blockchain traceability</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-700">Batch and transaction hashes with an append-only record model.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
